ğŸ” STEP 2 â€” Initialize Git Properly

Inside the project folder:

git init
git add .
git commit -m "Initial Vite React setup"

Now create your GitHub repo (empty, no README).

Then connect:

git remote add origin https://github.com/yourusername/portfolio.git
git branch -M main
git push -u origin main

Now your project is version-controlled from Day 1.
We commit after every meaningful step. Not random chaos commits ğŸ˜Œ

